	<h1>Acquisition basket/order creation</h1>
	<p>This page let you create or modify a basket. A basket contains as many order lines as you want.</p>
	<p>The 1st box contain the basket header : the librarian that started it, the date... It can be closed. A closed basket can't be modified anymore</p>
	<p>The 2nd box contain the order lines</p>
	<p>The 3rd box let you choose how to add a new order line. Each order line can come from :
	<ul>
		<li>An accepted suggestion</li>
		<li>An existing biblio (to order a new item)</li>
		<li>A completly new biblio (from scratch)</li>
	</ul>
